{"tid":2360741,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「港版輕井澤」粉嶺流水響人頭湧湧 　市民「打卡」散心","createTime":"2021-01-10T05:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T09:49:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11d87ddfc12f33248efcc5c43dfdabf2fc82cc8f","tid":2360741,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情近日有回落趨勢，但二人限聚令等社交措施未解禁，不少港人周末到郊外散心。以紅葉美景聞名，有「港版輕井澤」之稱的粉嶺流水響水塘，成為近期市民郊遊熱點。今早前往流水響的小巴站有逾百人候車，輪候人龍需要「打蛇餅」。<br />\n<br />\n至於流水響現場更見人頭湧湧，不少市民眼見美景當前放下戒心，三、五成群聚集，享受大自然風光，有人更脫下口罩拍照留念。有市民表示，疫情下生活壓抑，周末想到郊遊放鬆，並形容「唔郊遊好凄涼，喺屋企難過日子。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210109/424606248839680000319564.jpeg/-EROmRHqwCHDrmvBSmfPwNsrQDul4Um9AnTFuCR0xbg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210109%2F424606248839680000319564.jpeg%2F-EROmRHqwCHDrmvBSmfPwNsrQDul4Um9AnTFuCR0xbg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f0e39a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n流水響水塘的橙紅葉吸引不少市民拍照。（梁鵬威攝）<br />\n<br />\n早上11時，粉嶺港鐵站輪候前往流水響水塘的小巴站大排長龍，現場所見，至少有約150人排隊，人龍「打蛇餅」佔據旁邊兩個站頭。營辦商亦加密小巴班次，安排市民前往水塘。<br />\n<br />\n小巴營辦商職員林先生指，今早7、8時開始，前往流水響的小巴站已見人潮，到大約11時為更為高峰期，輪候小巴的人流不絕，故特別安排調動其他兩條線路的小巴支援，以疏導人潮，站頭同事亦須加班維持秩序。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210109/424607855107117056509431.jpeg/1pPZWa1hagpZ7gxxlN2qZ7zu0F3_3Bks-Qb08t8G9PI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210109%2F424607855107117056509431.jpeg%2F1pPZWa1hagpZ7gxxlN2qZ7zu0F3_3Bks-Qb08t8G9PI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9490d516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上11時，粉嶺港鐵站輪候前往流水響的小巴站大排長龍，估計有約150人排隊。（梁鵬威攝）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>坐圍封燒烤場休息用膳　人潮下脫口罩拍照</strong><br />\n<br />\n記者到流水響水塘視察，逗留約兩小時間，現場人頭湧湧，塘邊一樹一木，均是「打卡」熱點。有家長帶同子女觀賞紅葉，不少人亦忘卻二人限聚禁令，三五成群享受大自然風光，有人更脫下口罩拍照留念。因應疫情，港府已圍封的戶外燒烤場避免人群聚集，但有市民亦闖入燒烤場範圍，坐下休息及用膳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210109/424607603964776448418970.jpeg/KHqVaKr5AO9Z3AHrnb70Q-cAztgCgyX5wyklVOUpJVQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210109%2F424607603964776448418970.jpeg%2FKHqVaKr5AO9Z3AHrnb70Q-cAztgCgyX5wyklVOUpJVQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a8789d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民Janice 與友人帶同狗隻到流水響散心。（梁鵬威攝）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人狗戶外散心「唞氣」</strong><br />\n<br />\n市民余小姐與朋友一行五人，攜同愛犬到流水響郊遊。她表示，一直視愛犬如家人，疫情期間人、狗均要「唞氣」，趁周末到郊遊散心。對於社交距離措施近一個多月以來未有放寬，余小姐的同行友人Janice表示，「無辦法，港人都要面對，做好個人防疫。」<br />\n<br />\n與兄弟姊妹及友人一同郊遊的林先生表示，周末到郊外欣賞大自然，呼吸新鮮空氣，心情會更愉快。他又期望，若然疫情緩和情況許可，政府在農曆年假期間的防疫措拖勿過嚴，考慮彈性處理年宵市場，讓市民感受節日氣氛。與其同行的林婆婆表亦示，疫情下生活壓抑，周末要郊遊放鬆，「唔郊遊好凄涼，喺屋企難過日子。」"},{"pid":"40ee212dc9cda7125aba4fbd41ba13d6a51a1af3","tid":2360741,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"防疫撚快D慘叫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81ef2a2e1befbdded6af9ebdf5e7e6f257860d9","tid":2360741,"uid":42402,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bgu4Coe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgu4Coe.jpg&h=ccefc9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多人到 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fdbf162d8665e432bb8127c93e7c2ffe3fd085","tid":2360741,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec77a6171918d23a747a817c65d12f799274396f","tid":2360741,"uid":253223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:22:56.000Z","msg":"個景又幾靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90820a0ffc7e71d552e52aba3aa300b5d98b6545","tid":2360741,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a81ef2a2e1befbdded6af9ebdf5e7e6f257860d9","tid":2360741,"uid":42402,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bgu4Coe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgu4Coe.jpg&h=ccefc9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多人到 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"夏天隨時有人游水添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6ce9d2e7e9d221e8bc730df00e10e997e5ad84","tid":2360741,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"又係9假期？"},{"pid":"4cdc89e424b77fd59fd1b9eb5d28a1e5dc120535","tid":2360741,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"人迫人有乜好去"}]}